[
    {
        "english": "Lesson 1: Religious Education and the Buddha's teaching",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_1.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "A bird needs two wings in order to fly.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_2.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "If it possesses only one wing,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_3.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "it must remain on the ground",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_4.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and can never experience the joy of soaring.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_5.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "We also need two wings,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_6.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "which may be called the wings of education.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_7.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "One wing is secular education",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_8.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and the other is religious education.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_9.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "Without these two wings",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_10.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "we cannot hope to soar into the fields of knowledge",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_11.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "because we have little or no spiritual training.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_12.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "Religious education is necessary,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_13.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "for it teaches us how to think and act in order to be good and happy.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_14.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "It helps us to understand the meaning of life",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_15.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and to adjust ourselves to its laws.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_16.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "True religion means living the best and highest life,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_17.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "getting the most out of life,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_18.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "which makes a person light-hearted",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_19.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and joyful all the time.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_20.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "This is the sort of religion which the Buddha taught.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_21.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "It is true that we must attend classes in order to study his teachings,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_22.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "but the principal thing is to live them in our daily life.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_23.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "The Buddha teaches his followers to do good,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_24.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "to make the best use of life",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_25.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and tells them that his Path leads to true happiness",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_26.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "in this world and hereafter.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_27.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "Who was the Buddha?",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_28.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "There are many legends about the Buddha,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_29.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "but the Buddha was so great",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_30.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "that he had no need of legends to make him appear greater.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_31.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "He was the wisest teacher the world has ever seen",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_32.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and his teachings given to men over 2,500 years are still helpful to us today.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_33.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "He did not claim to be God,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_34.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "nor was he any divine messenger.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_35.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "He clearly told us",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_36.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "that if we listen carefully to his teaching",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_37.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "and walking his Path,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_38.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "we can achieve for ourselves",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_39.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "what he did for himself.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_40.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "Buddhism is truly a message of peace and happiness for everyone.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_41.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "Many of our brothers and sisters in the West",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_42.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "are taking refuge in the Great Master",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_43.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "who has guided the East for so many centuries.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_44.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "DHAMMAPADA VERSE 183",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_45.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "Not to do evil,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_46.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "To perform good,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_47.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "To purify one's mind,",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_48.MP3"
    },
    {
        "english": "This is the teaching of the Buddhas.",
        "audio": "../../courses/ENG101/lesson1/skill/audio/Religious_Education_and_the_Buddhas_Teaching_49.MP3"
    }
]